name: RoboPainter
description:
RoboPainter is the generic name for the class algorithms designed by a brilliant and esoteric group of people called functional programmers. Best RoboPainter will be awarded the honor medal of Leonardo Da Vinci, the RoboVinci Medal.

Do your best to get the Medal, if not then RoboPainter might whisper Da Vinci's last words “I have offended God and mankind because my work did not reach the quality it should have.”
